ou have not received an electronic notification that your poster or abstract was accepted, please email me at <strong>ashley.peeler@uncc.edu </strong>ASAP.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks and good luck!</p>','2013-05-23 17:11:29',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(133,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 16:55:53','duplicate discussions','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 16:55:53',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(134,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 16:55:54','duplicate discussions','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 16:55:54',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(135,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 16:55:56','duplicate discussions','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 16:55:56',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(136,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 16:55:57','duplicate discussions','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 16:55:57',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(137,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 17:18:06','dup. fix','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 17:18:06',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(138,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 17:18:07','dup. fix','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 17:18:07',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(139,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 17:18:07','dup. fix','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 17:18:07',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(140,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 17:18:09','dup. fix','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 17:18:09',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(141,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 17:18:09','dup. fix','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 17:18:09',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(142,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 17:18:09','dup. fix','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 17:18:09',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(143,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 18:25:26','test','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 18:25:26',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(144,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 18:25:28','test','<p>test</p>','2013-08-05 18:25:28',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(145,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 18:27:50','aa','<p>aa</p>','2013-08-05 18:27:50',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(146,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 18:27:51','aa','<p>aa</p>','2013-08-05 18:27:51',0,'{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(147,0,64,925,'2013-08-05 18:29:56','bb','<p>bb</p>','2013-08-05 18:29